 The second row of the ACTION DISPAY also features 3 icons. The first of these
 is to access the Mitteldorf Map. This is a smaller version of the map you 
 have been provided with, and lacks much of its detail. Most usefully, you can
 always find out where you are, since a flashing light will act as  'You are
